5d4b8468-838b-4654-acb7-23fd1743a568	ISP - Troubleshooting Cliente Sem Internet	Fluxo de diagnóstico quando cliente ISP reclama de sem internet: 1) Verificar se sessão PPPoE está ativa: /ppp active print where name=CLIENTE. 2) Se inativa: verificar autenticação nos logs /log print where message~"ppp". 3) Se ativa mas sem navegação: verificar rota default do cliente, testar ping 8.8.8.8 (conectividade) e ping google.com (DNS). 4) Se ping funciona mas navegação não: problema de DNS, verificar /ip dns print. 5) Se nada funciona: verificar NAT masquerade e uplink do provedor.	[-0.050689697,0.018051147,0.005191803,0.0072631836,0.0011587143,-0.0048446655,-0.029159546,0.015930176,0.06274414,0.008590698,0.02848816,-0.017303467,-0.042755127,-0.020050049,0.015434265,-0.0077438354,-0.04827881,0.025726318,-0.0602417,0.058807373,0.05154419,0.012451172,-0.0027885437,-0.008552551,0.0018510818,-0.020736694,0.018569946,0.010375977,0.046661377,-0.06719971,0.011131287,-0.026870728,-0.028152466,-0.008712769,0.017730713,0.025482178,-0.039031982,0.025253296,0.008636475,0.0012140274,0.0103302,0.020111084,-0.0063476562,-0.023040771,0.014083862,0.0060539246,0.011627197,-0.0014448166,0.056884766,-0.01386261,-0.015403748,0.04650879,0.0012960434,0.015808105,-0.0259552,-0.024047852,0.03555298,0.008453369,-0.013595581,0.019439697,0.03756714,0.022842407,-0.035888672,0.014694214,-0.03137207,0.048309326,0.0121536255,-0.023376465,-0.07086182,0.011581421,-0.047180176,0.04147339,0.011459351,-0.047729492,-0.0050811768,-0.010520935,0.015335083,0.0010356903,0.0033054352,0.0025424957,-0.04006958,0.019821167,-0.025787354,-0.025436401,0.029785156,0.008270264,-0.14562988,-0.042938232,-0.02078247,0.011764526,0.022613525,-0.014671326,-0.006072998,0.015151978,0.03186035,0.015640259,0.04537964,-0.007549286,-0.01914978,0.0009717941,0.056396484,-0.009513855,0.007610321,-0.00881958,0.0033340454,0.020599365,0.0003876686,0.0015420914,0.006214142,-0.013084412,0.057250977,0.008735657,-0.037994385,0.040985107,0.00255584